OL,3,CStarmer faces final Cabinet and PMQs
OL,4,Cas Burnham edges closer to No 10
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will face his last
OL,7,FCabinet and Prime Minister's
OL,8,FQuestions, while Andy Burnham nears
OL,9,Fthe Labour leadership finish line as
OL,10,Fnominations close on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe outgoing leader will hold farewell
OL,13,Ftalks with his senior ministers in
OL,14,FDowning Street before taking his last
OL,15,FCommons grilling at the despatch box
OL,16,Fat noon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
