OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784076511
OL,3,CStarmer faces final Cabinet and PMQs
OL,4,Cas Burnham edges closer to No 10
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Makerfield MP and prime
OL,7,Fminister-in-waiting Mr Burnham will
OL,8,Fedge closer to No 10 as nominations
OL,9,Ffor the Labour leadership formally
OL,10,Fclose on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe former Greater Manchester mayor's
OL,13,Fpremiership has already been cemented
OL,14,Fafter he received the backing of 369
OL,15,Fof the party's 403 MPs, making it
OL,16,Fmathematically impossible for a rival
OL,17,Fto enter the contest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
