CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784076511
OL,3,CStarmer faces final Cabinet and PMQs
OL,4,Cas Burnham edges closer to No 10
OL,6,FUnder Labour rules, candidates need
OL,7,Fthe backing of 81 MPs to stand in a
OL,8,Fcontest, meaning he is set for a
OL,9,Fcoronation.
OL,11,FThe outgoing Prime Minister, who will
OL,12,Fleave No 10 on Monday, told a
OL,13,Freception attended by campaigners
OL,14,Fwhose causes he had supported that
OL,15,Fthey had "made me who I am".
OL,17,FHe is spending his final days in
OL,18,Foffice highlighting what he sees as
OL,19,Fhis legacy ` support for Ukraine and
OL,20,Fchampioning domestic campaigns like
OL,21,Fthe Hillsborough Law.
OL,26,@wD@JOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
