CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784076511
OL,3,CStarmer faces final Cabinet and PMQs
OL,4,Cas Burnham edges closer to No 10
OL,6,FIn a sign of the closer relationship
OL,7,Fhe has tried to forge with European
OL,8,Fneighbours, he also attended Bastille
OL,9,FDay celebrations in Paris on Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith Emmanuel Macron, who awarded him
OL,11,Fthe Legion d'honneur in recognition of
OL,12,Fhis work with France on European
OL,13,Fsecurity.
OL,15,FSpeaking to reporters outside the
OL,16,FCommons later on Tuesday, his
OL,17,Fsuccessor Mr Burnham said people's
OL,18,Fcost of living was "the issue of our
OL,19,Ftimes" as he was quizzed on his plans
OL,20,Ffor government.
OL,26,@zD@TOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784076511
OL,3,CStarmer faces final Cabinet and PMQs
OL,4,Cas Burnham edges closer to No 10
OL,6,F"If we want to connect politics better
OL,7,Fwith people, well, let's deal with
OL,8,Fsome of the pressures people are under
OL,9,Fin terms of the everyday cost of
OL,10,Ftransport, the bills that they're
OL,11,Fpaying. I heard it so often on
OL,12,Fdoorsteps in the campaign," he said.
OL,14,F"You know, life has changed for
OL,15,Fpeople, and it's not necessarily got
OL,16,Fbetter. And I think we just need to be
OL,17,Frelentlessly focused on that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@[O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784076511
OL,3,CStarmer faces final Cabinet and PMQs
OL,4,Cas Burnham edges closer to No 10
OL,6,F"I have talked about more public
OL,7,Fcontrol of the basics, and then
OL,8,Fthrough that control, cutting the
OL,9,Fcost. I did that with buses in Greater
OL,10,FManchester, and I carry that same
OL,11,Fprinciple forward.
OL,13,F"To me, the cost of living and
OL,14,Freducing it is everything, and I think
OL,15,Fwe need to regain the confidence in
OL,16,Fthe public that we've got a credible
OL,17,Fplan to do that and make life better."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
