OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784076511
OL,3,CStarmer faces final Cabinet and PMQs
OL,4,Cas Burnham edges closer to No 10
OL,6,FThe former mayor nearly achieved a
OL,7,Fclean sweep of declared nominations,
OL,8,Fhad it not been for backbencher Neil
OL,9,FCoyle backing ex-minister Catherine
OL,10,FWest, who pulled back from mounting an
OL,11,Funlikely leadership challenge against
OL,12,FSir Keir in May.
OL,14,FBermondsey and Old Southwark MP Mr
OL,15,FCoyle said he had done so because he
OL,16,Falways nominates a woman and chose a
OL,17,Ffellow London MP who had previously
OL,18,Fsaid she wanted a contest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
